# 🎬 Fourier Transform Animation

Let me create a visual animation showing how a complex wave breaks into simple sine and cosine waves!

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fourier Transform Animation - Athena</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00dbde, #fc00ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .canvas-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .canvas-label {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .canvas-label .icon {
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        canvas {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: #0a0a1a;
            display: block;
        }

        .controls {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00dbde, #fc00ff);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-size: 1em;
            border-radius: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        button:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(252, 0, 255, 0.5);
        }

        button:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .speed-control {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #aaa;
        }

        input[type="range"] {
            width: 150px;
            accent-color: #fc00ff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #00dbde;
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            color: #00dbde;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .info-box p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .component-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin: 15px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .component-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 150px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .component-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .component-card .freq {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .component-card .label {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .c1 { color: #ff6b6b; }
        .c2 { color: #4ecdc4; }
        .c3 { color: #ffe66d; }
        .c4 { color: #a8e6cf; }

        .step-text {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 15px 0;
            min-height: 30px;
            color: #00dbde;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: opacity 0.5s;
        }

        .legend {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .legend-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        .legend-color {
            width: 20px;
            height: 4px;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 1.5em; }
            .component-card { min-width: 120px; padding: 10px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🌊 Fourier Transform Magic</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Watch how a complex wave breaks into simple sine & cosine waves</p>

        <div class="controls">
            <button id="playBtn">▶️ Start Animation</button>
            <button id="resetBtn">🔄 Reset</button>
            <div class="speed-control">
                <span>Speed</span>
                <input type="range" id="speedSlider" min="0.5" max="3" step="0.5" value="1">
                <span id="speedValue">1x</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-text" id="stepText">👆 Click "Start Animation" to begin</div>

        <!-- Complex Wave Canvas -->
        <div class="canvas-container">
            <div class="canvas-label">
                <span class="icon">🎵</span>
                <span>Complex Waveform (Time Domain) - What you hear</span>
            </div>
            <canvas id="complexCanvas" width="900" height="200"></canvas>
        </div>

        <!-- Component Waves Canvas -->
        <div class="canvas-container">
            <div class="canvas-label">
                <span class="icon">📊</span>
                <span>Decomposed Components - The "Ingredients"</span>
            </div>
            <canvas id="componentsCanvas" width="900" height="320"></canvas>
            <div class="legend">
                <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-color" style="background:#ff6b6b"></div> Component 1 (Low freq)</div>
                <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-color" style="background:#4ecdc4"></div> Component 2 (Medium freq)</div>
                <div class="legend
